          <p class="project-card-desc">Comprehensive club management system (Next.js 16 + Express 5 + Supabase) with 25+ API route modules, real-time Socket.IO, and RBAC across 16 staff roles. Features include restaurant POS with KOT system, inventory auto-deduction via standardized recipes, department invoicing with GST, WhatsApp payment receipts, member digital passport with QR cards, family affiliate management (up to 3 per member), AMC automation with Jan 15 lock rule, housekeeping with escalation, concierge ticketing with real-time chat, and an immutable financial ledger. Dual-node architecture with cloud + local SQLite shadow registry for zero data loss.</p>
          <div class="project-card-tech">
            <span>Next.js</span><span>Express</span><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>Socket.IO</span><span>TypeScript</span><span>Prisma</span>
