          <p class="project-card-desc">Built the official marketing website for The Stellaar Premium Family Club using Next.js 16 App Router and Framer Motion. Features a cinematic landing page with video background, membership tier showcase (Blue/Silver/Gold), lead capture form with WhatsApp redirect, rich blog system with TipTap editor, staff profiles, and Google Maps integration via Supabase + local SQLite.</p>
